# ELS telemetry (error + event logging). Build-time only — injected via vite.
# The ingest endpoint is hard-coded (https://api.insoweb.ru/els); only the API
# key is secret. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) for local builds, or set as a CI
# secret variable. Leave empty to disable ELS (the extension builds/runs fine).
#
# NEVER commit the real key. It belongs only in secret CI variables.
ELS_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the default endpoint (normally leave unset).
# ELS_ENDPOINT=
